  m_Text: "BY POULET GOURMAND / \nSARREMEJANE KOLLIAN\n\n\n\n\n\n3D ASSETS :\n\n\"Furniture
    Mega Pack - Free\" by dlgames\n\"Lowpoly Sports Car\" - 2 in 1 by IGIIID\n\"Simple
